Class Users

java.lang.Object
users.Users
public class Users extends Object
The Users constructor class creates a user attributes in the system. Each user has an ID, username, password, role, and optionally an associated customer ID. This class provides getter and setter methods for accessing and modifying user details, as well as a custom `toString` method for generating a string representation of the user.
Version:
5/1/2025
Author:
Amrit Singh
